{"tid":1095961,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]18+ 素人 初次 海下","createTime":"2019-04-07T11:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T19:29:45.000Z","uid":64601,"like":97,"dislike":401,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"3435a7bb82dfebd21ee80778f9cead3c5ea46cea","tid":1095961,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:41:33.000Z","msg":"今個星期行海下灣，路線大約係咁<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GOoMa7h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOoMa7h.png&h=a6cb7ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十一點彩虹搭11號小巴去西貢，再搭7號小巴喺海下落車。<br />\n<br />\n即刻開始！<br />\n<br />\n一開始會見到個WWF centre，可以book玻璃底船去睇珊瑚，$70 each，睇時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KoujwR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKoujwR6.jpg&h=77bde21c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Va7k0Mn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVa7k0Mn.jpg&h=c8192d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正式開始行山！<br />\n一開始見到忍刀三人眾，最後喺個袋拎咗塊牛扒佢哋就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RXXQDyd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRXXQDyd.jpg&h=dce50df7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我見地圖有小路點知生哂草，好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後成功出返大路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NYe7FPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYe7FPj.jpg&h=40fee455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F55bn2G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF55bn2G.jpg&h=9e102f2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZvKH0y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZvKH0y.jpg&h=3ad6bbca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到海下灣<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jzrWmc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jzrWmc.jpg&h=392e8c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNDHuGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNDHuGd.jpg&h=a1a42b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4gDPT8A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4gDPT8A.jpg&h=1fbe7451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5iToYAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5iToYAo.jpg&h=8adf45eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後兩三公里<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFHk0OR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFHk0OR.jpg&h=48b06ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VjmaDAK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVjmaDAK.jpg&h=b333c2b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感想：<br />\n條路多石，睇腳，同埋天氣好焗，好辛苦，行咗三個幾鐘，有海睇，天氣好啲可以好玩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會再去海下"},{"pid":"e069e77182336a9eda9eac758b481d99f35012f8","tid":1095961,"uid":131262,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"你每次行親天氣都好似唔係咁好噉"},{"pid":"c2d7746f20ee5c9d87628cd43fe0186fe7e59ca5","tid":1095961,"uid":58140,"like":292,"dislike":4,"score":288,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"0d204c6161657a3cc1cb0da56c6653d17a4f6a44","tid":1095961,"uid":10157,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2d7746f20ee5c9d87628cd43fe0186fe7e59ca5","tid":1095961,"uid":58140,"like":292,"dislike":4,"score":288,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T11:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e141a79adee2867bdf10d5b73f59652c31